<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />The heavens declare the glory of God,</para>

<para style="q1">and the skies make his handiwork known!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Day after day speech pours out;</para>

<para style="q1">night after night it reveals knowledge.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />There is no speech or spoken words;</para>

<para style="q1">their voice is not heard.</para>
